---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="The intersection of public policy and data science." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>The Architecture of Human Ambition</h1>
			
			<a href="/Keenan_Clough_CV.pdf" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: var(--accent); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 2em;">
				Download Full CV (PDF)
			</a>

			<p>
				I am driven by a singular focus: the intersection of human-centric governance and the technical architecture of the future. My goal is to design systems that allow for autonomy, resilience, and ethical operation in high-stakes environments.
			</p>

			<h3>The Foundation: Public Service & Policy</h3>
			<p>
				My background is rooted in institutional analysis and public service. During my tenure in the <strong>Civil Service (Ministry of Defence)</strong>, I navigated high-compliance environments and complex financial debt resolution. Combined with my academic foundation in Politics and historical research, I developed a deep understanding of multi-level stakeholder relationships and the "why" behind how we organise our world. 
			</p>

			<h3>The Pivot: Autonomous Systems & Data</h3>
			<p>
				I am now translating that strategic perspective into a hard technical toolkit. As a BSc Artificial Intelligence & Data Science undergraduate at the University of Lancashire, I am applying mathematical foundations and machine learning principles to solve complex, systemic problems.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				I thrive in the space where research, ideation, and technical execution collide. I do not just see raw data; I see the policy implications, the historical context, and the human impact.
			</p>

			<hr />

			<h3>Core Competencies</h3>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Data & Programming:</strong> Python (Pandas, Matplotlib), SQL (Oracle), Git/GitHub.</li>
				<li><strong>Systems & AI:</strong> Machine Learning Foundations, Systems Analysis, Database Design, Predictive Modelling.</li>
				<li><strong>Analysis & Visualisation:</strong> Power BI, Advanced Excel, Quantitative & Qualitative Research.</li>
				<li><strong>Operations:</strong> Stakeholder Management, Project Leadership, High-Compliance Governance.</li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>